name: Training
body:
### Core Training
[Mosaic Contributions](http://github.com/businessmentor/training/raw/master/Core Training - Mosaic Contributions - Gabrielle Monaen 21st November 2016 Romania.pdf) - Use this template to shape your work-in-progress. Why scatter ideas on notes and in blogs? Send it to colleagues for further work, or save it in final form and share it in PDF format. It makes managing the intellectual property easier, too.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
